typedef unsigned iMeshP_Part

typedef iBase_EntitySetHandle iMeshP_PartHandle

Since we allow overloading of iMesh functions' entity set handles with part handles, iMeshP_PartHandle must be defined the same as iBase_EntitySetHandle.

Types for classifying entities within a part.
